ey provide technical expertise and forensic support to aid in investigations.\n\n3. **Research and Development:**\n   - CSA invests in research and development to stay ahead of emerging cyber threats. This includes developing new tools and techniques for detecting and responding to cyber incidents.\n   - They also collaborate with academic institutions and industry partners to foster innovation in cybersecurity.\n\n### Reporting and Support:\n- If you suspect a cyber breach or encounter a cybercrime, you can report it to SingCERT through their official website or by calling their hotline. They will guide you on the steps to take and provide the necessary support to address the issue.\n\nBy taking a comprehensive approach that includes prevention, education, and robust incident response, CSA helps to safeguard Singapore’s digital landscape and protect its citizens and businesses from cyber threats."
