 for stronger anti-trafficking measures.\n\n7. **Be a Responsible Consumer**: Be mindful of the products and services you use and support businesses that have fair labor practices. Look for certifications and labels that indicate ethical sourcing and production.\n\nBy taking these steps, you can play a crucial role in combating human trafficking and making your community a safer place for everyone."
