uate funding and resources for anti-trafficking units within the SPF and other relevant agencies can enhance their effectiveness. This includes investing in technology, training, and personnel.\n\nIf you suspect any signs of human trafficking, it's important to report them immediately. You can contact the Anti-Human Trafficking Hotline at 9789 0000 for assistance. Together, we can work towards eradicating this heinous crime and protecting the vulnerable."
